data.description: DO NOT MISS THIS BEAR POINT OPPORTUNITY!! This home has been modernized throughout. One New HVAC system, flooring, countertops, paint, smooth ceilings. This home has plenty of space for a large family. Ground floor has separate living quarters so you could have total privacy from above floors. There is an entertainment space (man-cave) on the bottom level that can be used as an enclosed garage parking as well. Brand new decking in the fenced in backyard for added privacy. This home is just a block away from the water, neighborhood marina and restaurant. Separate laundry/washroom on bottom and main level. This is a rare find for the location.
